title: Roti Bakar
description: This is a popular Indonesian snack. The bread is usually thickly sliced, toasted, and then topped with a variety of sweet toppings like chocolate, cheese, or fruit jams.

title: Martabak Manis
description: This is a sweet, thick pancake filled with ingredients like chocolate, peanuts, cheese, or condensed milk. The batter is poured into a large pan, resulting in a fluffy, chewy texture.
